title: Delta Spirit - Ode to Sunshine
description:
I went and saw Delta Spirit at Jack Rabbits in Jacksonville, FL

For some asinine reason, their new record label would not let them sell any cd&#039;s until their new cd officially comes out in August. 

I liked them enough to open up audacity and capture all of the songs on their myspace page and break them up and label them. 

Folk/Rock Band

I believe the songs are off a discontinued album called &#039;Ode to Sunshine&#039; and will probably be a part of their new album when it comes out

Cheers
